    <div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > FuRyu [372 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/furyu">FuRyu</a> and developer <a title="Companies > AQURIA [135 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/aquria">AQURIA</a> have released the opening movie for <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/04/furyu-announces-school-life-rpg-varlet-for-ps5-switch-and-pc">newly announced</a> school life <a title="Genres > RPG [17,204 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/rpg">RPG</a> <em><a title="Games > VARLET [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/varlet">VARLET</a></em>, featuring the theme song “Shiori” sung by Aruka Arisaka voice actor Minori Suzuki and composed by wotaku. <span id="more-961464"></span></p><p><em>VARLET</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,356 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,015 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,021 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3406620/VARLET/" target="_blank">Steam</a> and <a title="Companies > Epic Games [349 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/epic-games">Epic Games</a> Store on August 28 worldwide.</p><p>Watch the opening movie below.</p><h2><span>Opening Movie</span></h2><p><strong>English</strong></p><p><iframe title="VARLET - OP Movie" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hphJnHnGtSk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><!-- AD: content -->
